headline: This Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stock Looks Set for a Second-Half Comeback
summary: AMD's upcoming MI400 release could be a game changer in the AI accelerator industry. This is especially true for stocks like Nvidia and Palantir Technologies, whose successes are responsible for the AI boom in large part.

headline: Prediction: 1 AI Stock Will Be Worth More Than Nvidia and Palantir Technologies Combined by 2030
summary: Nvidia and Palantir are currently worth a collective $4.5 trillion, but Amazon can surpass that figure within five years, which implies 100% upside for shareholders.  Amazon is a key player in three major industries, and the company is using artificial intelligence to improve profitability across its retail and cloud-computing divisions.  Wall Street expects Amazon's earnings to increase at 18% annually over the next three to five years, which makes the current valuation of 36 times earnings look reasonable.
